    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《深矿防线》中，你将深入一座尘封已久的矿洞，收集珍稀资源、建造强力设施、解救被困的英雄，并巧妙利用设施与英雄的协同效果抵御袭击。夜幕降临时，怪物将如潮水般涌来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标只有一个：在怪物狂潮中死守阵地，直至黎明！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/af4f869c85a3b0b41d54ec1f3220074e.avif?t=1771607750\" width=1200 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一天，你将派遣矮人矿工深入地下，展开有限次数的勘探，开采多个地块的资源。你只需精心规划最优路线，剩下的就交给勤劳的矿工吧！但切记不要贸然深入未知区域，毕竟谁也不知道，在黑暗深处潜伏着怎样的危险……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/387ae39eb51bc335f8a40b98ee4c362a.poster.avif?t=1771607750\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/387ae39eb51bc335f8a40b98ee4c362a.webm?t=1771607750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/7ebedfeefa632cd76fece8efa4a28c72.avif?t=1771607750\" width=1200 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理调配资源，建造独特功能设施；解锁设施蓝图，构筑高效协同体系。提升效率，巩固防御，向矿洞深处进发！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/82245cd9974b91e589133b3a7bf54561.poster.avif?t=1771607750\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/82245cd9974b91e589133b3a7bf54561.webm?t=1771607750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/07fffe82a2cec2da3de81d645087b878.avif?t=1771607750\" width=1200 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救被困矿洞的英雄，并用沿途发现的神秘符石和奇异果实强化英雄战力。解锁技能、提升属性，彻底释放英雄潜能，守护矿洞的每一夜安宁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/f230ed45d6bdb7a1fbe0348f74e02e7a.poster.avif?t=1771607750\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/f230ed45d6bdb7a1fbe0348f74e02e7a.webm?t=1771607750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/4932c63381f367cc9cc68a0d91bb8f6c.avif?t=1771607750\" width=1200 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分设施蕴藏着扭转战局的关键力量。合理部署防御工事，协同英雄构筑钢铁防线，让怪物大军止步于矿洞之外！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/2b7922844fd940ef4a1da1d9441ddbf4.poster.avif?t=1771607750\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164960/extras/2b7922844fd940ef4a1da1d9441ddbf4.webm?t=1771607750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12+超凡英雄，50+可解锁技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >75+功能各异的设施，每座具有独特的效果与技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+地块类型，等待你的勘探与发掘</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想了解&lt;&lt;深矿防线&gt;&gt;的最新资讯吗?加入玩家社区:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方1群：893670925</p>",
